{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create a responsive hero slideshow section with the following features:
    
    1. Multiple slides with add/remove functionality
    2. Separate image uploads for mobile and desktop that automatically switch based on screen size
    3. Text overlay with 9-position grid (top/center/bottom Ã— left/center/right) and customizable text color
    4. Button with customizable text, URL, positioning (9-position grid), and customizable button color
    5. Smooth slide transitions with navigation arrows and dots
    6. Flexible height settings with range slider from 0vh to 100vh for both mobile and desktop separately
    7. Width settings: 100% full width, custom percentages, and max-width constraints
    8. Full-width hero banner layout with images using object-fit: cover for consistent aspect ratios
    9. Mobile-responsive design that works seamlessly across all devices
    
    The height should be adjustable with a range slider allowing any value between 0vh and 100vh for precise control. The slideshow should be suitable for homepage hero sliders, campaign banners, and product showcase sections.
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
